{"tid":2285569,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"豬扒圖被列選舉資訊   FB人工智能審查爆笑料","createTime":"2020-11-14T08:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T09:24:28.000Z","uid":66271,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb1fef9fcd1b5dffcd0e704410b02001aac78a3","tid":2285569,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:14:28.000Z","msg":"社交平台透過人工智能，辨別被禁或敏感圖片。網路上從今年就一直流傳梗圖，細心一看就看到一塊長相極似美國總統特朗普的豬扒，當時大家只當它是一張有趣相片，隨便分享給其他朋友看。但最近在 Facebook 卻觸動了人工智能的審查機制，當你分享這張圖片時，會出現以下的提醒訊息：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/124768855_10221910175596379_3501225784247487187_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F124768855_10221910175596379_3501225784247487187_n.jpg&h=8cebe8fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分享相片時，FB 會發出「先查看最新選舉資訊再分享貼文」，要求用戶在分享之前，確認「你掌握的是正確資訊」，極有可能是觸發了 FB 人工智能的審查機制，在分享有關美國總統大選的帖文時，希望用戶能分享合符事實的「正確」資訊。當然現在大家會問，一塊豬扒怎會可能不是「正確」的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/124983597_2394461980700517_2925267369192980258_n-1-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F124983597_2394461980700517_2925267369192980258_n-1-1.jpg&h=ed9123aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cea754df7a8ec042fca47f739d2dd61d5b9b8067","tid":2285569,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba917e529b0552ee1c1686ce45b9267072dcf258","tid":2285569,"uid":19301,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"Trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d546f5d9e93288aa54175c91382bad70c90ca210","tid":2285569,"uid":49588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T08:30:42.000Z","msg":"美國都畀滲透得很徹底"},{"pid":"d4f58e2990481939080268a26026